97.8	Xeriscaping	Xeriscaping	Xeriscaping and xerogardening refers to landscaping and gardening in ways that reduce or eliminate the need for supplemental water from irrigation. It is promoted in regions that do not have easily accessible, plentiful, or reliable supplies of fresh water, and is gaining acceptance in other areas as climate patterns shift.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e2/Xeriscape03.png/100px-Xeriscape03.png
